----------------------------------------------------------
Flare OS Info                                  
----------------------------------------------------------
Ver 1.0                                                  
----------------------------------------------------------
Developers: Alex Yang, George Fang, William Wu
----------------------------------------------------------
Flare OS is a multi-thread OS, and it's a micro-kernel.
It's very simple, the struct is :
  void main()
{
  while(1)
 {
   func0(); //thread0
   func1(); //thread1
   func2(); //thread2
   func3(); //thread3
  }
}
Multi-thread use POSIX lib.
----------------------------------------------------------
To do it is very difficult for us at present.
Because we only have about 1-2 hours to program.
So we hope people who like it can join us and work with us.
